  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform routine administrative duties, maintaining all project files and filing quality records.</li><li>Procurement of construction materials and hardware.</li><li>Handle general admin tasks.</li><li>Provide clerical and administrative support to the project team.</li><li>Filing and maintaining up-to-date file records.</li><li>Accuracy in updating and maintaining the database of stock control records, schedule, VO/SOI and minute meetings.</li><li>Prepare project reports and submissions to the customer.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties assigned by the project management.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE \"A\" level</li><li>Minimum 2 years experience in the construction industry</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office</li><li>Able to communicate proficiently in English</li><li>Excellent interpersonal communication ability</li><li>Possess a positive attitude towards work and team oriented</li><li>Able to work independently and possess good team spirit</li><li>Able to operate AutoCAD is an advantage</li></ul><p><strong>What we offer:</strong></p><ul><li>5 days week</li><li>Medical benefits</li><li>Insurance</li><li>Company transport provided at Admiralty and Sengkang MRT</li></ul>",
